vivaldi-stealer is a Proof of Concept program which reads an unencrypted
logins, passwords and urls from a SQlite3 database of Vivaldi browser.

Platform.
Linux x86, x64.

Compilation.
make

Usage.
./vivaldi-stealer <login_data_path>

Sample output.
#1 record:
Login: cypher
Password: qwerty
Resource: https://domain.org/

#2 record:
Login: neo
Password: 12345678
Resource: http://the.matrix/

...
